				<li>s_quality -> radiant</li>
				<li>s_quality -> sacred</li>
				<li>s_quality -> hidden</li>
				<li>s_quality -> burning</li>

				<li>s_nature_deity -> tree of light</li>
				<li>s_nature_deity -> sky father</li>
				<li>s_nature_deity -> river christ</li>
				<li>s_nature_deity -> stone shepherd</li>

				<li>s_christ_title -> healer</li>
				<li>s_christ_title -> shepherd</li>
				<li>s_christ_title -> son</li>
				<li>s_christ_title -> fire-bearer</li>

				<li>s_elemental_force -> the winds</li>
				<li>s_elemental_force -> the waters</li>
				<li>s_elemental_force -> the sun path</li>
				<li>s_elemental_force -> thunder</li>

				<li>s_animal_or_tree -> eagle</li>
